queries.sql: SELECT rise_users.id, rise_users.user_type, rise_users.is_admin, rise_users.role_id, rise_users.email, rise_users.first_name, rise_users.last_name, rise_users.image, rise_users.message_checked_at, rise_users.notification_checked_at, rise_users.client_id, rise_users.enable_web_notification, rise_users.is_primary_contact, rise_users.sticky_note, rise_roles.title as role_title, rise_roles.permissions, (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(id) team_ids FROM rise_team WHERE FIND_IN_SET('1', `members`)) as team_ids FROM rise_users LEFT JOIN rise_roles ON rise_roles.id = rise_users.role_id AND rise_roles.deleted = 0 WHERE rise_users.deleted=0 AND rise_users.id=1

SELECT id, title, field_type FROM rise_custom_fields WHERE rise_custom_fields.related_to='expenses' AND rise_custom_fields.show_in_table=1 AND rise_custom_fields.deleted=0 ORDER BY rise_custom_fields.sort ASC

SELECT id, title, options FROM rise_custom_fields WHERE rise_custom_fields.related_to='expenses' AND rise_custom_fields.add_filter=1 AND rise_custom_fields.deleted=0 AND (rise_custom_fields.field_type='select' OR rise_custom_fields.field_type='multi_select') ORDER BY rise_custom_fields.sort ASC

SELECT rise_expenses.*, rise_expense_categories.title as category_title, CONCAT(rise_users.first_name, ' ', rise_users.last_name) AS linked_user_name, rise_clients.company_name AS linked_client_name, rise_projects.title AS project_title, tax_table.percentage AS tax_percentage, tax_table2.percentage AS tax_percentage2, accounts.account_name AS account_name FROM rise_expenses LEFT JOIN rise_expense_categories ON rise_expense_categories.id = rise_expenses.category_id LEFT JOIN rise_clients ON rise_clients.id = rise_expenses.client_id LEFT JOIN rise_projects ON rise_projects.id = rise_expenses.project_id LEFT JOIN rise_users ON rise_users.id = rise_expenses.user_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT rise_taxes.* FROM rise_taxes) AS tax_table ON tax_table.id = rise_expenses.tax_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT rise_taxes.* FROM rise_taxes) AS tax_table2 ON tax_table2.id = rise_expenses.tax_id2 LEFT JOIN accounts ON accounts.account_code = rise_expenses.account_code WHERE rise_expenses.deleted = 0 AND (rise_expenses.expense_date BETWEEN '2025-01-01' AND '2025-12-31')
